➜吸毒被捕娱乐圈普天同庆：他到底动了谁的奶酪？
http://www.sohu.com/a/337314933_407929	33166
<p class="ql-align-justify">著名娱乐圈搅屎棍黄毅清这次又又又又又被抓了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一个月前，他就因为和周立波网上开骂，多次发布不实言论，被警方行政拘留。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/97c2aa49129148f68e82836fa9033889.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">出来之后还写了封小学生手写体道歉声明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/09602d47a9154efc80af5e08f7be109f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而狗改不了吃x，这次他又因为寻衅滋事被拘留，而且警察叔叔还调查发现他吸毒贩毒，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/284d1fb0192a4723b8ab2026e54a5eec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然后娱乐圈上演了多年未见的普天同庆戏码。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黄奕一副岁月静好的样子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/0d54aa1003a54d03842d5727babb38cd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">周立波人狠话不多，三个手势说明了一切，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/6731cb1e0f5d4dd9a95641d19c2ab776.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">李小璐也忍不住在朋友圈大叹出了一口恶气。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/67b77740841d44099d4b6ea48894e664.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">而他碰瓷过的明星，其实远远不止这些。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/fe6dfc21f9034ce8903684f2f39d2fe0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黄毅清到底是如何成长为娱乐圈天字第一号过街老鼠的，且听我慢慢分解。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/ec77c9b57c7744b2a2c32b4c46f21a09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">（这就是传说中的黄毅清）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黄毅清之前是黄奕的前夫，两个人还在一起的时候，黄毅清也是本本分分的富二代模样。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/3bd3bd7ca477483e979a4ac8a224e93f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然而好景不长，两年后他们离婚了并且展开了撕逼大战。像是说黄奕是同性恋骗婚啊，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/19ac41f3e56445baaa365aa0fff10156.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">虐待孩子啊，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/4a8d007da87442b7a738a298ddf58c2d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">diss黄奕年纪大配不上自己啊什么的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/70167ec9d1b249338886ff8b684142c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">通过这场撕逼大战他发现自己蹦跶得越厉害就越有人关注，于是瞬间打通任督二脉开始表演。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">想起来就发些黄奕的私照。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/4ba97f1398414974b0dd72bf4e40764c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有以“黄奕亲口告诉我”来爆一些不知道真假的料。说黄奕跟每部戏的男主角都好过，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/57342229b6b54aecaa76dacec3f72726.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">比如GJJ，还说GJJ嘿咻的时候喜欢站着怎么证明……甚至拿他女儿发誓没瞎说。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/5f315f39ad42412b81caa0fbac1b90bf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有WZ没下限，见到功夫之王LLJ就跪下认干爹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/5fd52677ba3b4d3ebbcf507647653008.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">拍窃听的时候，shl把yx睡了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/a0ba12e230584e7599a0e7dfa9dbf41e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这些话题带给他热度和关注，粉丝数已经直逼黄奕了！！！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/7dbd8cb6775344738b726f1d0d339afd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/c44b6ef91d714c17b8feb0b09bbddc6d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">于是他越发热切地担任娱乐圈纪检委和第一狗仔，什么事都有他。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">李小璐PGone出事的时候，他一边在那里说什么贾乃亮好傻，好像自己和他很熟一样……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/a85649d119c64b499a60e9c24ecc5e5a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一边爆了PG One家庭信息，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/6fa0c2f3f7af42aab999c988bcb1ef79.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一边还说其实马苏和pgone也有一腿。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/5d0d823ab8984843b828ae3f1d00d4f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">事后把张继科也扯了进去，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/f2dd58b55a924a388bf7306597437940.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不过马苏张继科二话没说直接把他告上法庭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/830f927c39fd4810af93990a8e55b17e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他也说过崔永元出轨和别的女人同居，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/29f2e8474c9f4708a3981f12d5a0f5c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">之后被崔永元起诉了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/c7d880daae764d5a9893e3d0aefb8603.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他也造谣过薛之谦吸毒，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/81a4c40f64ee44b199d41166e01837ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">之后薛之谦火速去医院检查并且警察全程陪同啪啪打脸黄毅清，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/ffc75c2e89f34e74b2a41adf84dabf09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">但是黄毅清也许属于脸皮越打越厚的那种，他发微博表示：“只有吸过毒的人，才会对检验结果没有吸毒显得万分激动。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/3d5a82930fdb4f588700acf941397bd5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">？？？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再然后，就是最最有名的和周立波的大战了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黄毅清嘲笑周立波生不出孩子，女儿还是别人的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/0d1b3a10bc82438dbf4e7135a693832e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">立波老师就在粉丝群里面含沙射影地说黄毅清侵犯过他自己的女儿。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/b120c35e583542c3aef4feddbf5e7f34.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黄毅清继续不甘示弱表示，我女儿6岁你女儿16，你才更有可能侵犯你女儿。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/f636c95a8ce14030aaa2fae343e154b3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">黄毅清还说什么周立波某方面不行，又收了黑钱啦，而且回国就会接受尿检。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/bb6dd0dc90be4be3a3e1071ab947d3d5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">并且越吹越欢，说自己每条微博都有律师把关，从没打过败仗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/23a845283d114c86983433d4b1d0facc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">之前一副正义骑士的模样口口声声说要周立波验尿，最后搬起石头砸了自己的脚，黄毅清，out。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/b4f5f796c7c74c39b13bf784e31d2859.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">其实回到最开始，当个长相敦厚的圈外人有什么不好，但是为了那一点点噱头和关注就谎话谣言张口就来，成为一个洋洋自得跳梁小丑，以为我们看向他意味深长的目光里都是崇拜吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190829/2e39441754414252912d45149547e2fd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>